

d.geodesic - 

d.geodesic displays a geodesic line in the active @glossary("frame",16.glossary/graphframe.def) on the user's
graphics monitor.  This line traces the shortest distance between two
user-specified points on the curved surface of a longitude/latitude
data set.  Th two coordinate locations named must fall within the
boundaries of the user's current @glossary("geographic region",16.glossary/georeg.def).

